gle-Confession-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/GirlInRednew-single-Confession-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/GirlInRednew-single-Confession-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/GirlInRednew-single-Confession-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/GirlInRednew-single-Confession-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/girl-in-red">Girl In Red</a> has shared a brand-new single titled &#39;Confession&#39; – listen to it below.</p><p> The stripped-back, intimate track finds the Norwegian singer-songwriter (real name Marie Ulven) in a vulnerable and introspective mindset, and it is reminiscent of her lo-fi earlier work.</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/girl-in-red-taylor-swift-sabrina-carpenter-3616509">Girl In Red on &#39;I&#39;m Doing It Again Baby!&#39;: “It&#39;s ballsy, big dick energy”</a></strong></li></ul><p> Clocking in at under one-mintute-30-seconds, the song marks Ulven&#39;s first solo material since her 2024 album <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/girl-in-red-review-lyrics-tracklist-3616607">&#39;Doing It Again Baby!&#39;</a> 。</p><p> “ <em>There&#39;s a part of me nostalgic/ For all that has been/ There&#39;s a part of me that knows/ I wouldn&#39;t do it again</em> ,” Girl In Red ponders in hushed vocals over a raw, acoustic instrumental.</p><p> “ <em>There&#39;s a part of me that feels/ That I am reaching my end/ There&#39;s a part of me that knows/ It&#39;s my time to go/ I don&#39;t know if I can wake up/ Tomorrow morning/ And face my soul</em> .”</p><p> According to a press release, fans can expect more from Girl In Red “soon”. Check out the official &#39;Confession&#39; lyric video here: </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="girl in red - confession (Official Lyric Video)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Xi3cgot88A4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> The artist had <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGTub3XM2mU/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">teased</a> the new single on social media last week, when she shared a brief snippet and revealed the lyrics.</p><p> Girl In Red is set to appear at numerous European festivals this summer, including <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rock-werchter-2025-iggy-pop-underworld-and-gracie-abrams-lead-new-line-up-additions-3819822">Rock Werchter</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oya-2025-lola-young-mk-gee-beth-gibbons-bicep-lead-latest-additions-to-stacked-line-up-3838989">Øya</a> . She&#39;ll also <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-announces-her-biggest-ever-uk-show-at-bst-hyde-park-2025-3811479">open for Olivia Rodrigo at her BST Hyde Park show in London this June</a> . Next month, the musician will play various dates in Mexico and South America.</p><p> Meanwhile, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/girl-in-red-to-make-big-screen-feature-film-debut-in-maipos-low-expectations-3832836">Ulven is due to make her feature-length acting debut in the forthcoming film <em>Low Expectations</em></a> . She&#39;ll play lead character Maja – a 29-year-old artist who finds herself at breaking point following years of intense success.</p><p> The new movie is being produced by <a href="https://www.maipo.no/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Maipo Film</a> in Norway, in collaboration with <a href="https://www.snowglobefilm.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Snowglobe</a> in Denmark. It&#39;ll serve as the first feature from Norwegian director Eivind Landsvik. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Girl In Red | Firsts" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CN9crVsj9XI?start=114&enablejsapi=1#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> In <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/girl-in-red-review-lyrics-tracklist-3616607">a three-star review</a> , <em>NME</em> described &#39;Doing It Again Baby!&#39; as a “fine album; it&#39;s fun and sweet, if a little bland”. It added: “It&#39;s a pristine pop record that takes few risks and leaves little room for error – though it might be more interesting if it did.”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/girl-in-red-taylor-swift-sabrina-carpenter-3616509">Speaking to <em>NME</em> around the time of its release</a> , Girl In Red spoke about including a country breakdown on the record, and explained why she was trying out new sounds.</p><p> “Just because it&#39;s fun! I feel like on this album, I just want to have fun and I just want to do things because they&#39;re fun,” she said.</p><p> “And also sonically, I was like – this is fucking cool. It&#39;s fucking sick. I&#39;m just going with my intuition mostly. I can&#39;t read scores or notes, I don&#39;t know anything musically other than what I feel.”</p><p> She added: “It&#39;s so funny with the fucking banjo coming in. And then the top line being all, &#39;I&#39;m loving this new self-esteem&#39;. It&#39;s just ballsy, big dick energy.我只是用它。 And also, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">Beyoncé</a> just made a country song, so it&#39;s contemporary.”</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-girl-in-reds-vulnerable-new-single-confession-3842198">Check out Girl In Red&#39;s vulnerable new single &#39;Confession&#39;</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
